# Desktop environment packages
# Derived from docs/architecture.md — Session, Compositor, Shell Components,
# Terminal, Window Decoration, Display Manager, Lock Screen, Qt/GTK Bridging

# --- Session / Compositor ---
plasma-desktop
plasma-workspace          # includes KWin, KScreenLocker, System Settings
plasma-wayland-session
powerdevil
plasma-nm                 # NetworkManager applet
plasma-pa                 # audio applet
xdg-desktop-portal-kde    # Wayland portal support (screen share, file picker, etc.)

# --- Shell components (standalone, replacing Plasma's own panel/launcher/notifications) ---
waybar
mako

# rofi: mainline `rofi` has gained native Wayland support in recent releases
# (2.x). VERIFY at install time whether plain `rofi` covers KWin/Wayland
# correctly, or fall back to AUR rofi-lbonn-wayland if not.
rofi

# --- Terminal ---
konsole

# --- Window decoration ---
klassy                    # AUR — requires Plasma 6.3+ (current: 6.7.3, OK)

# --- Lock screen ---
# KScreenLocker ships with plasma-workspace above — customized, not replaced

# --- Display manager ---
sddm

# --- Qt/GTK bridging (docs/architecture.md) ---
qt6ct
kvantum                   # provides Kvantum + kvantum-qt6 style engine
nwg-look                  # AUR — GTK theme applier for Wayland

# --- Fonts (docs/design.md typography) ---
ttf-inter
ttf-jetbrains-mono-nerd
ttf-cinzel                # AUR — verify exact package name at install time
